latestIgtvVideos.caption:
BOOGIE YOUR WAY INTO THE HOLIDAYS 🪩🕺 with our new, ultra-groovy haircare sets 🎁. If you’re clients are looking for a gift to give (or to keep for themselves 😉) these are it! 

Can you guess what the theme for our gift sets was this year? Let us know below! ⬇

#Matrix #MatrixHair #GiftIdeas #Holiday #GiftInspo #TotalResults

We’re always down for a color transformation 😍. 

Thanks @stylebyvega for showing us your pretty stylist swag 💕! 

#MatrixColor #ColorWithConfidence #HairMeme #Hairstylist #HairstylistLife #HairTransformation

BRING ON THE BRONDE 🙌. Not too warm 🔥, not too cool ❄ (Autumn 🍁 vibes anyone?) this transformation proves going lighter isn’t just for the summer. To achieve this look, #MatrixPartner @treehousehair used Open Air Pre-Bonded to lighten and SoColor Sync 7NGA to tone.

Drop a 🤎 if you love this transformation as much as we do!

Formula:
Pre-Lighten: Open Air Pre-Bonded + 30 Volume (9%)
Tone: SoColor Sync Pre-Bonded 7NGA + 10 Volume (3%)

#BabyGotBronde #BalayageOnPoint #MatrixOpenAir #SoColorSync #ClayLightener #MatrixColor

COOL FOR THE SUMMER🧊! @hairby_gloria beat the heat ☀ with this cool ❄ ashy #balayage using #SoColorSync Pre-Bonded shades 5N, 4A, 8G, and 10V. She protected the integrity of the hair⛓ by using our products that already have the bonder added! We 💙 this versatile color placement so the color pops any style!

Are you team curled or straight on this look 💇‍♀️?

#BetterBeacauseItsPreBonded #Matrix #MatrixColor #ColorWithConfidence

Formula:
Pre-Lighten: Light Master + starting with 15 Volume Developer, working up to 35 Volume Developer
Shampoo: Unbreak My Blonde
Base Toner: SoColor Sync Pre-Bonded 1:1 5N + 4A
Mids & Ends Toner: SoColor Sync Pre-Bonded 1:4 8G + 3:4 10V

👋👋👋 Light Master, Light Master Pre-Bonded, and Lift +Tone would like to introduce the NEWEST ADDITION to our lightener fam, Open Air Pre-Bonded! Our newest love is made with kaolin clay, lifts up to 7 levels, and saturates and forms to the hair’s natural bends. Now we’ve got all your lightening needs under one roof 💓! 

💙 Light Master ─ Ideal for classic lightening techniques.
💜 Light Master Pre-Bonded ─ Lifts up to 8 levels + has the added protection of a bonder already in the formula. 
💗 Open Air Pre-Bonded ─ Clay texture that’s perfect for brush or hand painting (also has the bonder already added!).
💚 Lift + Tone ─ Toned highlights in 10 minutes. 

Give a like if you love our lightener portfolio 🌈!

#LightMaster #MatrixOpenAir #Lightener #BlondeWithConfidence

BRUNETTE = BLUE SHAMPOO! @fredecutshair cooled her client down by using #BrassOff to neutralize those orange undertones. The blue pigment combats that orange 🟠❌ in just ONE application.

Do your brunette clients still use purple shampoo? For best results, they should use blue 💙!!

#BlueShampoo #PurpleShampoo #Balayage #BrunetteBalayage #BlondeBalayage #IcyHair #CoolTones #Toning

INCLUSIVITY FOR ALL ❤️. “Pride is the freedom to be yourself and have the same opportunities.” Well said @cristianulate_ 👏👏! #MatrixFam – with us, you have a home all-day every day 🌈.

#PrideMonth #Quotes #AllHairTypesAllHuman #CelebrateAll #LoveIsLove

BRONDE, BABY BRONDE 🤎. @brinaesingingstylist has got that #bronde goin’ on 😍. Using NEW #SoColorSync Acidic Pre-Bonded shades 9NGA and 7NGA she created a natural lived-in look with a neutral gold ash reflect + protected her client’s hair without having to add a bonding additive in the formula (because its Pre-Bonded!). Just look at that golden closeup ✨!

Drop a 🌈 if you already got your hands on some of our new SoColor Sync NGA shades!

Formula:
Base: SoColor Sync Pre-Bonded 3N + 10 Volume (3%)
Toner: SoColor Sync Acidic Pre-Bonded 1:1 7NGA + 9NGA+ 10 Volume (3%)
Money Piece: SoColor Sync Acidic Pre-Bonded 9NGA + 10 Volume (3%)

STOP, *CHOP* & ROLL!! 💇‍♀️✂

Client's coming in for a fresh cut? Make like @artistry_by_gabriel, from the Matrix Mentor Me program, and use our Miracle Creator multi-tasking leave in treatment as your cutting lotion. It instantly detangles hair, conditions, adds shine and smooths frizz (on top of that it's also suitable for all hair types & textures). If this multi-benefit spray doesn't leave you believing in miracles, we don't know what will! ✨

What’s your favorite way to use our Miracle Creator spray?! 💕 Comment below and there's a chance you may just get a surprise 👀

IT’S A DEMI DREAM COME TRUE 🤩! Don’t sacrifice the strands for good coverage, now you can get both! Super coverage meets super protection with our ✨ upgraded ✨ alkaline demi, Super Sync! 
 
💖 Say arrivederci to baby grays because this formula has 100% gray coverage on clients with up to 50% gray hair with ONLY 10 Volume (and no ammonia 😉)
💖 Say willkommen to FOUR new NN shades that cover 100% of grays on clients with up to 75% gray hair (and still with 10 Vol!) 
💖 Say salut to our new pre-bonded complex for INSTANT fiber protection 
💖 and Say OMG to 103% shinier hair* 

The SoColor Sync formula you know (and 💗) just got SUPER! 

Available in Europe and coming to the U.S. in 2025. Check our stories for all market availability. 

*vs unwashed uncolored hair

#MatrixColor #SuperSync #SoColorSync #WarmHair #NewHairProduct #ColorWithConfidence #DemiColor

BILLION BOND CARE FOR BILLION DOLLAR HAIR! 💸💰💗

Maxed out on damage? 💳 Meet new Instacure Build-a-Bond! 💗🧬 Bursting with 1 BILLION BONDS inside every bottle to fight damage, our formulas are infused with citric acid to strengthen hair from the inside, while squalane softens the outside. The result? Stunning strands that are 8x stronger! Now that hair, she is SO money honey! 💪💰💵

•Vegan Formula : No Animal Derived Ingredients
•Free from SLS/SLES
•Formulated without phthalate

Go grab it today @ultabeauty 🫶. Rolling out at @saloncentric on 8.26 and other retailers in September.
